meta.title: Adam for Hire #4: The Able Sisters (part 2)
meta.desc: The second part to the fourth episode.

ttsdata.text: Hi Adam! Do you have a knife?
I hate to break it to you, sweetheart, but I don't have a knife. But, what would you need it for if I had one?
Well, I just vandalized Amos Slade's house and Sheriff Sam Brown's after me, so I need to hide here. Can I?
Of course, Lila. Anything for my girlfriend! I can't believe that wanker of a sheriff is after you for doing the right thing. Hide behind the trousers!
Hopefully that wanker Sheriff Sam Brown won't come here.
